{"tid":698143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家是咪唔撚記得be water my friend?","createTime":"2018-06-11T12:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T11:44:12.000Z","uid":148,"like":69,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6275b06a46b347cdb3174214d05134b69c4beaaa","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"本土、獨派元氣大傷 士氣低落唔幫手都算撚數喇<br />\n踩多兩腳真係唔撚知咩心態<br />\n日日150個蝗落嚟 已經赤化得好嚴重<br />\n連由生活開始抗赤化都好似攞咗你地條命咁<br />\n叫你地講少啲支那蝗語又屌<br />\n整埋list俾你地睇有咩紅色資本入侵又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩假膠玩野都唔該你睇吓咩事喇屌<br />\n平時抽吓水都算<br />\n但大事當前仲跟班五毛癲 跟埋佢地講野真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由雨革失敗到立法會dq <br />\n呢幾年發生嘅事 的確好撚灰、好無力<br />\n但大家好似唔撚記得咗be water my friend<br />\n一到逆境波就唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次又一次無吸收失敗嘅教訓,又唔撚識參考過去成功嘅例子<br />\n成班剩係識小學雞式屌嚟屌去<br />\n2018年啦,2047未到都就快玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每個人能力底線都唔同 <br />\n而家休養生息 咪各有各做<br />\n政策、文宣叻嘅咪寫多啲、交流多啲<br />\n講野叻又唔怕面對群眾嘅咪開街站集吓氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錯,做咩都無撚用、政府都唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢走嘅咪移民<br />\n無錢走嘅又唔想俾支共政府強姦嘅咪盡自己能力做<br />\n唔知幾時開始大家模糊哂勇武抗爭<br />\n唔是乜都鳩衝 而係睇形勢做適當嘅野<br />\n雨革個時大家都識be water 而家就忘記得一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由雨革到而家 以前高登都發揮住一個重要嘅角色<br />\n而家連登點解唔試吓做其他野,反五毛都好過咩都唔做<br />\n食放題到對抗水貨客 甚至二創惡搞諷刺時弊<br />\n大家唔記得哂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有唔少昔日戰友雖然各散東西,但仲有好多巴打喺唔同崗位努力緊<br />\n有啲就去咗獨派、本土派做文宣/創黨<br />\n有班仲喺前線默默耕耘緊 各自喺自己個區搞吓街站<br />\n既然仲有咁多人都未肯放棄 大家一灰嘅時候咪互相支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你承擔唔到後果 咪做啲你能力範圍做到嘅野<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n連小小野都唔肯去做嘅 要等死又散播失敗主義真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟自己都有過情緒病 絕望、想死都有,慶幸身邊有人拉一把走返出嚟<br />\n而家個大環境就好似有情緒病咁 需要有人拉一把、幫手互相支持<br />\n但我相信呢個病一定會慢慢好返 既然需要啲時間好返<br />\n點解唔爭取喺有限時間討論點去醫呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家仲記得當時雨革、佔旺、魚革係點嚟<br />\n唔好忘記be water 呢條路唔通就變通行第二條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcf7e2fd38671fac4edf61dac90f86522f63960","tid":698143,"uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"好多五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c8baf0f704adef6e98e2e938ad0a8ff157ca27","tid":698143,"uid":34884,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"留名睇班街童搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d6dfd9d1095f064c89a1e3802759286420a378","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a42c119b867fb31efd5fc15191e38d3dac08ff1","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba665c1105fe23e6c01838ef88d9beaa9fef223","tid":698143,"uid":103207,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"連今日都仲玩膠抽梁天琦水既撚樣,<br />\n<br />\n唔撚得閒慢慢分係5毛定玩膠,一律block9晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3c5c90ff272bf2c1cc8de9c8c69bd6ef6e2f5e","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba665c1105fe23e6c01838ef88d9beaa9fef223","tid":698143,"uid":103207,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"連今日都仲玩膠抽梁天琦水既撚樣,<br />\n<br />\n唔撚得閒慢慢分係5毛定玩膠,一律block9晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f209a7590f7dded000006f00625dff8710e1d7d1","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b132a69479ad6ba80c250d16906091805432832c","tid":698143,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"而家個大環境就好似有情緒病咁 需要有人拉一把、幫手互相支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d474d66312db5a3910219f1b4cdf539b6e4b89","tid":698143,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"而家d「獨派」唔幫佢捉5毛都要畀佢地屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同佢意見又話打手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b15e4da2b70cf38e398c049914ef1f7fa36c2cb","tid":698143,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084947af7eb78c25089c758058785